        <updateDate>2020-06-09T13:00:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Restore and Modernize Our National Labs Act </b></p> <p>This bill provides funding to the Department of Energy (DOE) for deferred maintenance, critical infrastructure needs, and modernization of National Laboratories. </p> <p>DOE shall submit, with the annual budget submission of the President through FY2025, a list of projects for which DOE will provide funding under this bill.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
